- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the mutual control of position/coordination in scenarios where drones may encounter obstacles, which is a problem related to systems and control.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The module can be used for studying the mutual control of position/coordination, which can involve AI techniques such as path planning and obstacle avoidance.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The module may involve computer vision techniques for detecting obstacles and other objects in the environment.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages): The paper mentions the emphasis on API consistency and ease of use, which can be related to programming language design and implementation.
